ock and Roll Music.\"", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Cover Me&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Cover Me", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/cover-me/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/rrmusic.jpg?fit=1200%2C1182&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/rrmusic.jpg?fit=1200%2C1182&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/rrmusic.jpg?fit=1200%2C1182&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/rrmusic.jpg?fit=1200%2C1182&ssl=1&resize=700%2C400 2x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/rrmusic.jpg?fit=1200%2C1182&ssl=1&resize=1050%2C600 3x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 61328, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/11/14/kingdom-of-days-november-10-2/", "url_meta": {"origin": 68954, "position": 3}, "title": "Kingdom of Days: November 10", "author": "Ken", "date": "November 14, 2025", "format": false, "excerpt": "Not one but *two* Springsteen box sets were released on this date: Live 1975-85 and Tracks. Plus: a Billy Joel guest appearance, a Daily Show interview, and more.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Kingdom of Days&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Kingdom of Days", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/kingdom-of-days/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/trackslive.jpg?fit=706%2C382&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/trackslive.jpg?fit=706%2C382&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/trackslive.jpg?fit=706%2C382&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/trackslive.jpg?fit=706%2C382&ssl=1&resize=700%2C400 2x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 13812, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2019/10/22/cover-me-tortoise-and-bonnie-prince-billy-thunder-road/", "url_meta": {"origin": 68954, "position": 4}, "title": "Cover Me, Tortoise and Bonnie &#8220;Prince&#8221; Billy: Thunder Road", "author": "Ken", "date": "October 22, 2019", "format": false, "excerpt": "Perhaps the most surprising and effective re-interpretation of \"Thunder Road\" ever, Tortoise and Bonnie \"Prince\" Billy transform Bruce's classic song of escape into a dark, sinister temptation.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Cover Me&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Cover Me", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/cover-me/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/bonnie.jpg?fit=500%2C500&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200}, "classes": []}, {"id": 63005, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/12/13/kingdom-of-days-december-13-2/", "url_meta": {"origin": 68954, "position": 5}, "title": "Kingdom of Days: December 13", "author": "Ken", "date": "December 13, 2025", "format": false, "excerpt": "On this date: Bruce joins Paul Simon and an all-star line-up to combat homelessness, the E Street Band plays the entire Darkness album to an empty theater, and more.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Kingdom of Days&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Kingdom of Days", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/kingdom-of-days/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/boston92.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/boston92.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/boston92.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-